include them as part of the design and in the relevant specification sections rather than adding requirements 
to this section.</NPR><BRK/>
<BRK/>
<NPR>Note that use of small local UPSes creates additional maintenance burdens due to the requirements for periodic 
battery replacement and may ultimately result in a less reliable system.</NPR><BRK/>
